\begin_layout Chapter
Structure
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "chap_structure"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A thesis must be a coherent document of a research project, not a collection of loosely connected pages. This chapter walks through the typical structure of a thesis from cover to cover, and discusses the aim and content of each part. Sections 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec_coverpage"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 through 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec_declaration"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 describe the mandatory pages that must be included in each thesis.
\end_layout

