\begin_layout Section
Task description
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The task description covers some background information about the thesis, lists the major steps during the work, and specifies the deliverables of the thesis. It can be seen as a contract between the student and the supervisor or the company and is the basis for grading. Therefore, students should make sure the listed tasks are reasonable to be finished within the time constraints. Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:task"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 shows an example of this page.
\end_layout

