name "sec_declaration"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Students are required to sign the declaration of the thesis provided by THL (see Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:declaration"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

), which includes 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
after ""
before ""
key "kun08"
literal "false"

\end_inset

: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The fact that she or he writes the work independently without outside help. 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The fact that she or he has used only the cited sources. 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The fact that she or he agrees with a publication of the work. 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The first two items are mandatory while the last one is optional. Pay attention that some students working in companies are required to sign a Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) with the companies, and some companies do not agree to publish the thesis work. In this case, the last paragraph must be removed from the declaration.
\end_layout

